{
  "stem": "9503.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And also, we sang a German song.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I really don't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The-- in-- in-- in both Westerbork and in-- in Theresienstadt, there was, at one time, sort of like a cabaret.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, there was an awful lot of pretend, and there was, I think, a lot of grown-ups apparently needed to find their escapes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so whatever I was exposed to and-- and remembered, shortly after the war I must have written it down.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some of it is-- is very almost tongue in cheek.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a-- a Westerbork alphabet poem that each letter described a camp condition.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was done in a semi-humorous way rather than totally heavy, but the heaviness comes through anyway.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There-- there were some songs that were sung in German in Theresienstadt, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] some of them just showed some of the relationships that went on between men and women, and apparently these continued.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And some-- there was-- is one that is-- is very sad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and, you know, when I look at it now, then I realize that people wrote this, and they knew something.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It's in German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I can try to translate it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's called 'Ade, Day Kamerad,' 'Good-bye, Comrade.' [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Here splits our thread, because tomorrow I have to leave.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I will part from you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "One drives me from here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I am going on the Poland transport.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You were so good to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You gave me much courage.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You were always ready to help.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I had-- what do you call it-- when you pressed my hand, it took the worries away.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
